Create Slicers and Format the page Color 13

Create Slicers and Format the page Color

Format the page Color

Steps

1.      Go to Format Pane

2.      Select the Page background Icon

3.      Select Gray Color (White 20% darker shade)

4.      Adjust Transparency to 22%



Create the following Slicers;

·       Year

·       Room Type

·       Neighborhood

·       Neighborhood Groups

Steps

1.      Select Slicer visual

2.      Go to the Fields pane

3.      Drag and Drop District Year into the Field pane

4.      Drag and drop Room Type into the Field pane

5.      Drag and drop Neighborhood into the Field pane

6.      Drag and drop Neighborhood Groups into the Field pane

7.      Go to the Format pane, Off Slicer header and On the Title, type in Title text and change the Background color.


·       Year Slicer



·       Room Type Slicer
